  - guid: 87739e86-e700-4019-9e3e-91668e676da8
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Hello co-worker. I am Katoro. Please do not be afraid.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I do not want to hurt you. I am just doing my job.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 263.5, y: 197.5}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: ae3f10fd-385c-4bc1-9d26-229d8bd2a4dd
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Is this your first time fighting? Oh no. If I can
        give you any advice, please tell me.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 698.5, y: 197.5}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 5be46824-e66b-4df5-8add-edd32ae6e6de
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: To be honest, it is pretty fun when my rival knows
        what they are doing. I like a tough battle.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I do not like hurting the helpless.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Sometimes I feel bad for the people paying us all
        that money to fight. But Aya says they deserve it.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Some girls manage to defeat me without getting help.
        I think that is really cool and impressive.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: But Aya gets really mad when that happens.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I'm not sure what she does to them, but I never see
        these girls again on the next day.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1282, y: 334.5}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 7dec4e37-fef0-487e-8645-aefdcab4a4f7
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'Please watch me closely. Every time I am going

        to
        attack, you can tell by my body movements.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: DODGE to get out of the way. It should be pretty
        simple.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: You can also try to PARRY my attacks by BLOCKING
        at the correct time.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'This leaves me open to your

        counter-attacks.
        But it is harder than dodging.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: If you get disoriented, try using the CAMERA LOCK-ON.
        It keeps your vision on me at all times.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I will go as easy on you as I can. Unfortunately,
        they have programmed me to try and win.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Please don't let yourself get hurt. I hope you're
        strong.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1282, y: 53.5}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
